'''伊祖沙·加拿·古爾'''（{{lang|en|'''Idrissa Gana Gueye'''}}，{{bd|1989年|9月26日||}}），是一名[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]的職業足球運動員，司職[[防守中場|防守中場]]，現時效力[[法國甲組足球聯賽|法甲]]球會[[巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部|巴黎圣日耳曼]]，并代表[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞内加尔国家队]]出战国际比赛。

== 球會生涯==
===早期生涯===
[[File:Corchia,_Eto'o,_Gueye.JPG|thumb]]]]

古爾於[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]][[達喀爾|達喀爾]]出生。在2008年改投[[里爾奧林匹克體育會|里爾]]前，他曾為迪雅宝罗斯（Diambars FC）上陣<ref name = NFT>{{NFT player|pid=45752|accessdate= 2015-07-02}}</ref>。2010-11賽季，古爾成為里爾一線隊的成員，並贏得該季的法甲聯賽冠軍。隨後的4季裏，他於聯賽和[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐洲聯賽冠軍盃]]的比賽中皆為球隊的正選球員<ref name = "EFC">{{cite web|url=http://www.evertonfc.com/players/i/ig/idrissa-gana-gueye|title=Profile|accessdate=2016-09-22|language=en|publisher=Everton F.C.|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606191042/http://www.evertonfc.com/players/i/ig/idrissa-gana-gueye|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===阿士東維拉===
2015年7月10日，古爾轉會至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英超]]球會[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，轉會費為約900萬鎊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.avfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10265~4855398,00.html|title=Breaking news: Villa sign Gueye|date=2015-07-10|accessdate=2015-07-10|publisher=Aston Villa F.C.|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317150521/http://www.avfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10265~4855398%2C00.html|archivedate=2016-03-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33362759|title=Idrissa Gueye: Aston Villa sign Lille midfielder for undisclosed fee|date=2015-07-10|accessdate=2015-07-13|publisher=BBC Sport|language=en|archive-date=2015-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731225731/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33362759|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3168190/Aston-Villa-midfielder-Idrissa-Gueye-admits-club-s-desire-sign-helped-ignore-Southampton-Marseille.html|title=Aston Villa midfielder Idrissa Gueye admits club's desire to sign him helped him ignore from Southampton and Marseille|accessdate=2017-07-10|publisher=Daily Mail|language=en|archive-date=2019-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222182622/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3168190/Aston-Villa-midfielder-Idrissa-Gueye-admits-club-s-desire-sign-helped-ignore-Southampton-Marseille.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該季，他為球隊上陣35場比賽，但球隊於聯賽排名第20，下季需於[[英格蘭冠軍足球聯賽|英冠]]作賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Idrissa Gueye: Aston Villa cannot keep midfielder after release clause triggered|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36904124|accessdate=2017-06-05|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=2016-07-27|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111092953/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36904124|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===愛華頓===
2016年8月2日，[[愛華頓足球會|愛華頓]]啟動古爾合約中的解約條款，與球員簽約4年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36904124|title=Idrissa Gana: Aston Villa cannot keep midfielder after release clause triggered|date=2016-07-27|accessdate=2016-07-30|publisher=BBC Sport|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111092953/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36904124|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36958094|title=Idrissa Gueye: Everton sign midfielder from Aston Villa|date=2016-08-02|accessdate=2016-08-02|publisher=BBC Sport|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701071954/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36958094|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2016年，古爾成為歐洲五大聯賽中攔截及鏟球成功次數最多的球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/01/chelseas-ngolo-kante-surprisingly-only-second-in-tackles-made-in-2016-6355184/|title=Chelsea's N'Golo Kante surprisingly only second in tackles made in 2016|date=2017-01-01|accessdate=2017-01-01|publisher=Metro|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111112707/https://metro.co.uk/2017/01/01/chelseas-ngolo-kante-surprisingly-only-second-in-tackles-made-in-2016-6355184/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/evertons-idrissa-gueye-best-ball-12407013|title=Why Everton's Idrissa Gueye is the best ball-winning midfielder in Europe|date=2017-01-04|accessdate=2017-01-04|publisher=Liverpool Echo|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112054603/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/evertons-idrissa-gueye-best-ball-12407013|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/row-zed/evertons-idrissa-gueye-statistically-best-9563709|title=Everton's Idrissa Gueye is statistically the best holding midfielder in the whole of EUROPE|date=2017-01-04|accessdate=2017-01-04|publisher=Mirror|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109144645/https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/row-zed/evertons-idrissa-gueye-statistically-best-9563709|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年2月25日，古爾在聯賽對陣[[新特蘭足球會|新特蘭]]時攻入轉會後首球，協助球隊在主場以2比0勝出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39012183|title=nEverton 2-0 Sunderland|date=2017-02-25|accessdate=2017-02-25|publisher=BBC|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205032623/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39012183|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他是2016-17賽季歐洲五大聯賽中最快成功攔截100次的球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/club/everton/368/blog/post/3069681/everton-finish-off-sunderland-as-idrissa-gueye-and-morgan-schneiderlin-continue-to-gel|title=Idrissa Gueye, Morgan Schneiderlin class as Everton beat Sunderland|date=2017-02-27|accessdate=2017-03-05|publisher=ESPN|language=en|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912093622/http://www.espnfc.com/club/everton/368/blog/post/3069681/everton-finish-off-sunderland-as-idrissa-gueye-and-morgan-schneiderlin-continue-to-gel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯 ==
2011年，古爾首次代表[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞内加尔国家队]]上陣<ref name=NFT/><ref name = "FIFA">{{FIFA player|332314}}</ref>，曾代表球隊於[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會男子足球比賽|2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會男子足球比賽]]<ref name = "FIFA"/>、[[2015年非洲國家盃|2015年非洲國家盃]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30743603|title=2015 Africa Cup of Nations: Sadio Mane included in Senegal squad|date=2015-01-09|language=en|accessdate=2015-07-02|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223233751/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30743603|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[2017年非洲国家杯|2017年非洲国家杯]]上陣。

[[2019年非洲國家盃|2019年非洲國家盃]]及[[2021年非洲國家盃|2021年非洲國家盃]]連續兩屆幫助球隊進入決賽，[[2021年非洲國家盃|2021年非洲國家盃]]也跟者球隊奪下國家隊首座冠軍金盃。

